_sText:
This is my favourite map, I have spent more time on this map that i have on my VCE homework for the year (if you knew me you'd now assume this map was crap).

Nevertheless I have poured as much as my newbie mind can handle into this map.

Please, give me feedback, i want to know if I am worth anything to this world, if I recieve no feedback I will assume you all want me dead and take my life so I won't bother you again.


(back to the map) It is CT biased i think but i tried to even it as much as possible.

I hope you like my map as much as I do  ('do' that means if this message is 50 years old I still love my map more than my saggy wife)

(Also thanks to XxLeXuSxX for all the help teaching me how to use hammer and thanks to all the random pplz who provided ideas for it.)
